{"tid":1714232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好塞將軍澳翠林","createTime":"2019-11-13T00:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:00:26.000Z","uid":220583,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6146d9042d6ad2ffd70f45485dc9051598954092","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:20:23.000Z","msg":"翠林地理位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FT0m78W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFT0m78W.jpg&h=eabab917&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oej7jfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foej7jfD.jpg&h=1b749c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞咗TKO真係變孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時班藍絲港真係會醒就唔好啦"},{"pid":"ce4d41e4ce248d91d4ab5c698279387aa8377636","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:20:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c6a2a00c86ec04c29381cbb663c4ab496dbf793b","tid":1714232,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千其唔好塞啊 會番唔到工"},{"pid":"237b7eafea5f51c8e4fb3b5fe8ca9b64620f1a58","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"自推十次(1/10)"},{"pid":"84bce0cb5f6f972e0a7afd970e5831ba2e2f1f29","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"100092b4635e14528a99eefef205a5bb4a564121","tid":1714232,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:22:22.000Z","msg":"而家要返既都返咗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69cd6b7cdf440819ef6331ee53db94bb04303fc","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:22:22.000Z","msg":"(3/10)"},{"pid":"b3cc0af2fff349c844cfa1d57965c39463b68c55","tid":1714232,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d6087eadb2d6c565753cf9099eb41af6a70207","tid":1714232,"uid":278228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:23:17.000Z","msg":"借po一個位<br />\n大家好，示威其實都4個月<br />\n我地每次行動都會影響到民生，<br />\n琴日我係沙田去暴大，<br />\n沿途好多街彷屌road block，又話過分乜乜77<br />\n但冇人提過黑警好似殺人咁攻中大<br />\n因為呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持<br />\n<br />\n策略：小隊突擊，人在明我在暗<br />\n<br />\n要救中大就要有大啲話語權，宜家有話語權既係官"},{"pid":"fb264728f717169edb6861d6a27732b6a0b88de4","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:23:18.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851137fb4127ff262d1e176fa28beb00cffe9dca","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:24:29.000Z","msg":"翠林點都重要過尚德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9be30666614858f33fe5b3a9c78371de9eb5df0","tid":1714232,"uid":220583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:25:05.000Z","msg":"(6/10)"},{"pid":"7b169a2e91b14812b96f8fb1f15444b71f0ef457","tid":1714232,"uid":185731,"like":0,"dislike"